<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ shuō guò 迦南654</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shuō guò bù pà fēng chuī yǔ dǎ, nǐ shuō guò gān xīn bèi zhǔ shí zì jià.
 nǐ shuō guò gēn zhǔ shén me dōu bù pà, nǐ shuō guò yī dìng yào ráo shù tā.
 zhǔ a nǐ lái bāng zhù wǒ men, shuō dào yě néng zuò dào,
 tīng dào yě néng xíng dào. bù zài qī piàn zì jǐ,
 yīn wèi shí hòu bù duō le, yīn wèi tiān sè yě bù zǎo le.
 hòu miàn de rén yǐ yuè guò le wǒ men wǒ men kuài jǐng xǐng ba.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>654</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>